				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Tuy%C3%AAn/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-%C3%94n-Tuy%E1%BB%81n/poem-Mu0zqUa9vXRevJivtIZgVQ">Đề Ôn Tuyền - 題溫泉</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Tuy%C3%AAn/author-tLEZwqQ5URDVKx36CILUiQ">Tiết Tuyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/%C4%90o%E1%BA%A3n-ca-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-43Lf49JtQxAUhD_uQQ76eA">Đoản ca hành kỳ 2 - 短歌行其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/author-eKAWfrr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Ti%E1%BB%81m/H%C3%A1n-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-mSH9PE5CreDWAB83y1xujw">Hán tướng hành - 漢將行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-RNpImmo2Zi_8n8IJeKR5eg">Thẩm Đức Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0-Ho%C3%A0i/Kim-L%C4%83ng-t%E1%BA%A1p-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-TjsjzUUHp0l84UYd1kvs4A">Kim Lăng tạp cảm - 金陵雜感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0-Ho%C3%A0i/author-vNnaqt-fFSRtea3LIoxFOg">Dư Hoài</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/L%E1%BB%A5c-ch%C3%A2u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u/poem-BgKpaQpu2juLQERndzbyhA">Lục châu ca đầu - 六州歌頭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-77k7d_i26Q3zI_gu_1iz-w">Trương Hiếu Tường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/S%E1%BA%AFc-t%E1%BB%A9-T%C3%BA-Phong-t%E1%BB%B1-bi/poem-xxLxY7z4rcP4cV-gZh2gaw">Sắc tứ Tú Phong tự bi - 敕賜秀峰寺碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/author-_vSGbKXOej4AgRYmpqgykw">Hồ Nguyên Trừng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Tr%C4%83n/T%C3%A1i-h%E1%BA%A1-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-17roGQcwgaPYID_R1SVsYw">Tái hạ kỳ 2 - 塞下其二</a> (<a href="http